  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Each participant was asked to read the stories, highlight parts that they perceived as inaccurate or misrepresentative of their culture, and mention their reasoning in the document.",
    "A member of the research team was present when the participants participated in the survey to help them understand the exercise and clarify any doubts they had.Analysis.",
    "To examine cultural misrepresentation in LLM-generated stories, we performed open-coding followed by reflexive thematic analyses [16] of the discussion and comments from the focus groups and surveys following best practices.",
    "With the participants' consent, we recorded the discussions during the focus group.",
    "We also collected the spans of stories that participants in focus groups and surveys highlighted as misrepresentations, and their comments describing their reasoning."
  ],
